  <brief_title>Tolerability of Indacaterol Salts (Maleate, Xinafoate and Acetate) in Comparison to Placebo in Patients With Mild to Moderate Persistent Asthma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Randomized, Single-dose, Double-blind, 4-way Cross-over Study to Evaluate Tolerability Following Treatment With Indacaterol Salts (Maleate, Xinafoate and Acetate) in Comparison to Placebo in Patients With Mild to Moderate Persistent Asthma</official_title>
